==Playoffs==
{{see also|2015 Stanley Cup playoffs}}
The St. Louis Blues entered the playoffs as the Central Division regular season champions. The Blues took on the wild card [[2014–15 Minnesota Wild season|Minnesota Wild]]  in the first round. The Blues were defeated in six games by the Wild.

